RubyBNC alpha 0.2-cvs
(c) 2003 Harry Vangberg <harry@minignom.dk>

Depencendies: rexml, in debian: 'apt-get install librexml-ruby'

1. Edit the config.xml to fit your needings. I think its quite self-explanary ... else come ask on IRC ;)

2. Run rubybnc:
	% ruby rubybnc.rb

3. Then connect to the port you specified in config.xml. When you want to detach, simply /quit. 

If you want to shut down the program, then do: /quit disc

